Class CustomerAddress

java.lang.Object
CustomerAddress
public class CustomerAddress extends Object
Address class

This class represents a customer address. It holds a constructor for creating an address object. This class also holds getters and setters for retrieval and modification of an address object.

Since:
Corretto-17
Version:
1.0
